author: Home RenoVision DIY
description:
I tested DeWalt’s PowerStack and FlexVolt batteries in a real demolition scenario, cutting straight through a car with the reciprocator saw. This is the kind of jobsite test that exposes torque, runtime, and power in a way specs never do. Watch the full DeWalt battery comparison on the channel now.
